56.4	Emeril_Lagasse	Emeril Lagasse	Emeril John Lagasse is an American celebrity chef, restaurateur, television personality, and cookbook author. A regional James Beard Award winner, he is perhaps most notable for his Food Network shows Emeril Live and Essence of Emeril as well as catchphrases such as “Kick it up a notch!” and “Bam!” The "Emeril Empire" of media, products and restaurants generates an estimated US$150 million annually in revenue.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6e/Emeril_Lagasse_book_signing.jpg/220px-Emeril_Lagasse_book_signing.jpg
